HEADWORD: Onerous
<hw>On"er*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>onerosus</ets>, fr. <ets>onus</ets>, <ets>oneris</ets>, a load,
burden: cf. F. <ets>on⟦eacute⟧reux</ets>.]</ety> <def>Burdensome;
